task-rest_bold.json.TaskDescription: Scan sessions started with the acquisition of the anatomical scan, followed by two task-related fMRI runs, a DTI scan and finally, the resting state scan.
task-rest_bold.json.Instructions: Participants were given access to a specific training and instruction video http://www.kuleuven.ac.be/radiology/FTP/Instructie_MRI.wmv. We also used standard written and verbal description at consent form time as well as verbal instructions prior to and during scan session.
